data.name: inducesDataGridView.ToolTip
data.value: Recipes to be executed when a recipe concludes whilst this aspect is present. Chance is an integer from 0-100 When additional is checked, a new verb token is spawned. Otherwise, it hijacks the current verb.

data.name: extendsTextBox.ToolTip
data.value: When specified, the game will copy properties of the aspects specified here onto the currently open aspect. Processed left to right. If using more than one ID, separate them with commas but no spaces. "example1,example2,example3"
